    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy. The exterior has several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional head unit. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable oil leak and the transmission shifts roughly, so I would recommend towing it or having a mechanic inspect it before any long-distance travel. This is a project car suited for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
