      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous, climate-controlled preservation. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paint, adheres to the highest standards of aesthetic and mechanical integrity. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
